    { q: "Do I need permits for bathroom remodeling in Houston?", a: "Yes, most bathroom remodels in Houston require permits, especially if you're moving plumbing, electrical, or walls. We handle all permit applications and inspections as part of our service." },
    { q: "What's the average cost of bathroom remodeling in Houston?", a: "In Houston, bathroom remodels range from $3,000 for basic updates to $30,000+ for luxury renovations. Mid-range projects typically fall between $10,000-$20,000. We offer options for every budget." },
    { q: "Can I live in my home during bathroom remodeling?", a: "Yes, most clients remain in their homes during remodeling. We work efficiently to minimize disruption. If you have only one bathroom, we can coordinate with neighbors or suggest alternatives." },
    { q: "Do you help with fixture selection?", a: "Absolutely! We provide guidance on fixture selection based on your needs, bathroom layout, and budget. We have partnerships with major brands and can often secure better pricing." }
  ]} />
  
